    <briefdescription>
<para>classe <ref refid="classFlux__interfacial__base" kindref="compound">Flux_interfacial_base</ref> correlations de flux de chaleur interfacial de la forme </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim> Phi_{kl} = h_{kl}(T_k - T_l)
